subject: Basketball
NCAA Basketball Tournament
lead_paragraph: Josh Duell scored 16 pointsto lead Siena past No. 20 Stanford, 79-67, in a game reminiscent of the Saints’ stunning victory against the Cardinal in the 1989 N.C.A.A. tournament.
